WEBVTT

00:00:11.010 --> 00:00:15.570 line:80%
[One month later]

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:22.840 line:80%
Stop crying!

00:00:23.160 --> 00:00:25.000 line:80%
Keep crying and I'll cut off your tongues!

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:25.860 line:80%
Did you hear me?

00:00:32.360 --> 00:00:32.890 line:80%
Who is it?

00:00:33.800 --> 00:00:34.960 line:80%
I'm a butcher.

00:00:35.480 --> 00:00:37.800 line:80%
A butcher? There are no pigs here.

00:00:39.560 --> 00:00:41.490 line:80%
Aren't there 3 right in front of me?

00:01:28.560 --> 00:01:31.040 line:80%
Ever since that Butcher Beauty
from Jizhou got famous,

00:01:31.040 --> 00:01:33.400 line:80%
girls love carrying a knife
when they go out.

00:01:33.400 --> 00:01:34.800 line:80%
They say it wards off evil.

00:01:34.800 --> 00:01:35.720 line:80%
Exactly.

00:01:36.240 --> 00:01:37.720 line:80%
These young ladies nowadays

00:01:37.720 --> 00:01:39.279 line:80%
really believe that nonsense.

00:01:39.279 --> 00:01:40.480 line:80%
Every girl traveling far

00:01:40.480 --> 00:01:42.080 line:80%
dresses up like this.

00:01:42.520 --> 00:01:43.040 line:80%
Look.

00:01:43.600 --> 00:01:45.880 line:80%
These days, the human traffickers,
robbers,

00:01:45.880 --> 00:01:48.480 line:80%
village bullies, and local ruffians

00:01:48.680 --> 00:01:49.680 line:80%
are most afraid of

00:01:49.800 --> 00:01:52.460 line:80%
meeting a pretty girl
carrying a butcher knife.

00:01:53.880 --> 00:01:55.040 line:80%
Little lady.

00:01:55.640 --> 00:01:57.400 line:80%
It's beautiful. Let me see.

00:02:05.160 --> 00:02:06.760 line:80%
The Bu-Butcher Beauty!

00:02:06.760 --> 00:02:07.680 line:80%
Run! Run!

00:02:12.320 --> 00:02:14.480 line:80%
Thank you. Thank you, Butcher Beauty!

00:02:15.600 --> 00:02:16.879 line:80%
Look, a poor imitator.

00:02:17.560 --> 00:02:18.760 line:80%
Stop talking nonsense.

00:02:18.760 --> 00:02:20.040 line:80%
If you ran into the real one now,

00:02:20.040 --> 00:02:22.320 line:80%
you'd deserve to be castrated on the spot.

00:02:22.320 --> 00:02:23.000 line:80%
Perverts.

00:02:23.440 --> 00:02:24.800 line:80%
Full of filthy language.

00:02:24.800 --> 00:02:25.800 line:80%
Just ignore them.

00:02:25.920 --> 00:02:26.650 line:80%
Look at this.

00:02:35.200 --> 00:02:36.320 line:80%
What about Fan Changning?

00:02:36.320 --> 00:02:38.450 line:80%
Is there someone named Fan Changning?

00:02:39.040 --> 00:02:40.570 line:80%
There's no one by that name.

00:02:41.000 --> 00:02:41.840 line:80%
Next.

00:02:43.280 --> 00:02:44.080 line:80%
Changning,

00:02:44.960 --> 00:02:46.120 line:80%
where are you?

00:02:47.140 --> 00:02:56.450 line:80%
[Missing Person Notice]
[Announcement]

00:02:47.600 --> 00:02:49.060 line:80%
I've saved so many people.

00:02:49.920 --> 00:02:51.379 line:80%
Why still can't I find you?

00:02:52.560 --> 00:02:55.480 line:80%
Yan Zheng, if only you were here.

00:02:56.520 --> 00:02:58.000 line:80%
The world is so vast.

00:02:58.920 --> 00:03:00.360 line:80%
Where are you?

00:03:12.320 --> 00:03:13.000 line:80%
Go away!

00:03:13.880 --> 00:03:15.080 line:80%
Are you disobedient?

00:03:17.520 --> 00:03:19.180 line:80%
I told you not to go over there.

00:03:19.840 --> 00:03:21.500 line:80%
Go the other way. Understood?

00:03:26.200 --> 00:03:26.920 line:80%
Changning!

00:03:27.160 --> 00:03:28.240 line:80%
Stop!

00:03:39.400 --> 00:03:40.560 line:80%
Don't hit my father!

00:03:40.560 --> 00:03:42.160 line:80%
Don't hit my father!

00:03:43.200 --> 00:03:44.040 line:80%
Who are you?

00:03:44.040 --> 00:03:45.520 line:80%
Why did you hit me?

00:03:48.840 --> 00:03:49.760 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:03:51.600 --> 00:03:52.400 line:80%
Sorry.

00:03:53.000 --> 00:03:54.280 line:80%
I thought you were a trafficker.

00:03:54.280 --> 00:03:55.240 line:80%
A trafficker?

00:03:55.240 --> 00:03:57.240 line:80%
I think you're a trafficker!

00:03:58.120 --> 00:03:59.280 line:80%
I'm going to report you!

00:03:59.280 --> 00:04:00.760 line:80%
I'm going to report you!

00:05:28.370 --> 00:05:33.880 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:05:33.959 --> 00:05:36.459 line:80%
[Episode 20]

00:05:41.860 --> 00:05:45.690 line:80%
[Region of Baxia]

00:05:44.560 --> 00:05:46.080 line:80%
Once we pass this boundary marker,

00:05:46.080 --> 00:05:47.640 line:80%
it is the territory of our Sui family.

00:05:46.290 --> 00:05:48.980 line:80%
[Region of Baxia]

00:05:49.240 --> 00:05:51.370 line:80%
The common folk call this place Baxia.

00:05:51.920 --> 00:05:53.600 line:80%
Legend says the dragon has nine sons,

00:05:53.600 --> 00:05:55.530 line:80%
and one of them looks like a turtle,

00:05:55.600 --> 00:05:57.920 line:80%
with immense strength,
able to stir up rivers and seas.

00:05:57.920 --> 00:06:00.780 line:80%
Only Yu the Great
tamed it during his flood control.

00:06:01.680 --> 00:06:04.280 line:80%
My father granted me
this strategic territory,

00:06:04.280 --> 00:06:05.960 line:80%
and I renamed it Baxia,

00:06:07.160 --> 00:06:08.560 line:80%
hoping it

00:06:08.920 --> 00:06:10.250 line:80%
would live up to its name

00:06:10.840 --> 00:06:11.970 line:80%
and be unbreakable.

00:06:13.080 --> 00:06:15.280 line:80%
Isn't that just a big turtle?

00:06:18.360 --> 00:06:20.760 line:80%
The Dragon's son is a big turtle.

00:06:22.840 --> 00:06:24.280 line:80%
Pearls before swine.

00:06:25.440 --> 00:06:26.160 line:80%
Keep up.

00:06:26.280 --> 00:06:27.740 line:80%
The terrain is so low here.

00:06:27.920 --> 00:06:29.250 line:80%
What if there's a flood?

00:06:33.560 --> 00:06:34.220 line:80%
We're here.

00:06:43.680 --> 00:06:49.470 line:80%
[Sui]

00:06:52.480 --> 00:06:54.560 line:80%
Welcome back to the manor, Your Highness!

00:06:52.560 --> 00:06:54.700 line:80%
[Sui]

00:07:02.320 --> 00:07:04.720 line:80%
Welcome back to the manor, Your Highness!

00:07:07.800 --> 00:07:10.200 line:80%
Welcome back to the manor, Your Highness!

00:07:17.600 --> 00:07:20.400 line:80%
Take my bros to the guest rooms
and treat them well.

00:07:20.400 --> 00:07:21.000 line:80%
Yes.

00:07:21.480 --> 00:07:22.000 line:80%
This way, please.

00:07:22.000 --> 00:07:23.460 line:80%
Thank you, Your Highness.

00:07:28.670 --> 00:07:34.780 line:80%
[Heroic Spirit]

00:07:33.040 --> 00:07:34.970 line:80%
Let's go. What are you waiting for?

00:07:35.200 --> 00:07:37.800 line:80%
You really are Lord Changxin's
heir apparent.

00:07:38.320 --> 00:07:39.160 line:80%
Yes.

00:07:39.600 --> 00:07:40.860 line:80%
Who did you think I was?

00:07:42.200 --> 00:07:43.860 line:80%
I thought you were lying to me.

00:07:51.640 --> 00:07:52.400 line:80%
Min!

00:07:52.690 --> 00:07:54.480 line:80%
[Victorious in Every Battle]

00:07:53.959 --> 00:07:54.720 line:80%
Yuanqing.

00:07:55.640 --> 00:07:56.440 line:80%
Min,

00:07:57.520 --> 00:07:58.520 line:80%
how have you been?

00:07:59.000 --> 00:07:59.960 line:80%
I'm doing well.

00:08:00.400 --> 00:08:02.130 line:80%
You've worked hard, Yuanqing.

00:08:16.480 --> 00:08:18.080 line:80%
I need to speak with Yuanqing alone.

00:08:18.080 --> 00:08:19.000 line:80%
Take them away.

00:08:19.080 --> 00:08:19.720 line:80%
Yes.

00:08:19.730 --> 00:08:22.630 line:80%
[Victorious in Every Battle]

00:08:22.360 --> 00:08:23.120 line:80%
Please.

00:08:24.360 --> 00:08:25.120 line:80%
Let's go.

00:08:27.290 --> 00:08:32.300 line:80%
[Victorious in Every Battle]

00:08:28.000 --> 00:08:29.520 line:80%
Let's talk inside.

00:08:36.040 --> 00:08:37.700 line:80%
A scout reported this morning

00:08:37.839 --> 00:08:41.000 line:80%
that Xie Zheng raided
our Chongzhou grain route last night.

00:08:41.000 --> 00:08:43.000 line:80%
I'm afraid Father won't hold out
much longer

00:08:43.000 --> 00:08:44.330 line:80%
at the front in Lucheng.

00:08:44.480 --> 00:08:46.320 line:80%
How did Xie Zheng
penetrate deep into Chongzhou

00:08:46.320 --> 00:08:47.720 line:80%
without anyone knowing?

00:08:48.280 --> 00:08:49.680 line:80%
How many men did he bring?

00:08:50.160 --> 00:08:51.820 line:80%
No more than a hundred riders.

00:08:54.960 --> 00:08:56.040 line:80%
Damn it.

00:08:56.520 --> 00:08:59.000 line:80%
It will take at least a month
to repair the grain route.

00:08:59.000 --> 00:09:00.280 line:80%
You mentioned before

00:09:00.280 --> 00:09:02.440 line:80%
that we should send guards
for the grain route.

00:09:02.440 --> 00:09:03.800 line:80%
But Father rejected it.

00:09:04.920 --> 00:09:05.840 line:80%
What a pity.

00:09:10.080 --> 00:09:10.720 line:80%
By the way,

00:09:11.320 --> 00:09:13.520 line:80%
who were those two just now?

00:09:16.200 --> 00:09:18.720 line:80%
The older one is my woman,

00:09:19.560 --> 00:09:22.400 line:80%
and the younger one... is a big surprise.

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:39.640 line:80%
I thought he'd kill the mother
and keep the child.

00:09:39.640 --> 00:09:42.920 line:80%
I didn't expect him to plan
to kill the child and keep the mother.

00:09:42.920 --> 00:09:44.450 line:80%
He really is soft-hearted.

00:09:45.360 --> 00:09:46.600 line:80%
I didn't expect...

00:09:47.040 --> 00:09:49.240 line:80%
Min to be just like the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:09:51.840 --> 00:09:52.880 line:80%
Only you

00:09:53.400 --> 00:09:54.720 line:80%
could be so heartless.

00:09:57.520 --> 00:09:58.760 line:80%
Me? Heartless?

00:10:02.960 --> 00:10:04.440 line:80%
As long as you stay with me,

00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:06.800 line:80%
I can give you anything you want.

00:10:08.720 --> 00:10:09.760 line:80%
Then I want

00:10:10.840 --> 00:10:13.800 line:80%
the heads of Xie Zheng and Fan Changyu.

00:10:16.080 --> 00:10:16.840 line:80%
Okay.

00:10:17.840 --> 00:10:18.840 line:80%
It's a deal.

00:10:30.480 --> 00:10:31.960 line:80%
Do you still hate me now?

00:10:39.440 --> 00:10:41.570 line:80%
I don't want to think about it anymore.

00:10:42.400 --> 00:10:43.720 line:80%
After tonight,

00:10:43.960 --> 00:10:46.090 line:80%
I'll decide whether or not to hate you.

00:10:55.330 --> 00:10:58.400 line:80%
[Yanzhou Army Camp]

00:11:03.880 --> 00:11:05.140 line:80%
Thanks for pulling off

00:11:05.200 --> 00:11:06.060 line:80%
the diversion.

00:11:06.720 --> 00:11:08.380 line:80%
No need to be so polite with me.

00:11:08.560 --> 00:11:09.760 line:80%
How will you repay me?

00:11:10.720 --> 00:11:11.580 line:80%
Forget I asked.

00:11:12.640 --> 00:11:14.200 line:80%
As for He Jingyuan,

00:11:14.360 --> 00:11:17.160 line:80%
he broke the siege of Lin'an for you,

00:11:17.520 --> 00:11:20.050 line:80%
and you raided the grain route
to buy him time.

00:11:20.160 --> 00:11:21.290 line:80%
I guess you're even.

00:11:21.520 --> 00:11:22.780 line:80%
By the way, the bundle.

00:11:26.320 --> 00:11:28.320 line:80%
Someone asked me to give this to you.

00:11:41.400 --> 00:11:42.240 line:80%
Candy?

00:11:43.200 --> 00:11:44.880 line:80%
I thought you hated sweets.

00:11:47.520 --> 00:11:48.320 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:11:48.480 --> 00:11:50.140 line:80%
You won't even let me touch it?

00:11:54.430 --> 00:11:57.260 line:80%
[Divorce Agreement]

00:12:05.520 --> 00:12:07.520 line:80%
[The wife, Fan Changyu, native of Jizhou,
now wishes to part]

00:12:07.520 --> 00:12:10.240 line:80%
[from her husband,
Yan Zheng, native of Chongzhou.]

00:12:10.270 --> 00:12:12.530 line:80%
[Wife: Fan Changyu]
[Husband:]

00:12:16.000 --> 00:12:17.400 line:80%
We are even?

00:12:19.440 --> 00:12:20.280 line:80%
Fair enough.

00:12:27.760 --> 00:12:29.560 line:80%
Where did this bundle come from?

00:12:30.280 --> 00:12:33.080 line:80%
Mr. Zhao pulled some strings
to get it sent up here.

00:12:34.280 --> 00:12:35.610 line:80%
He was conscripted too?

00:12:36.320 --> 00:12:37.320 line:80%
But don't worry.

00:12:37.640 --> 00:12:38.680 line:80%
It stops with me.

00:12:39.720 --> 00:12:41.320 line:80%
He won't find out who you are.

00:12:47.040 --> 00:12:48.080 line:80%
Pass on the order.

00:12:49.080 --> 00:12:50.940 line:80%
Don't let him go to the front line.

00:12:51.040 --> 00:12:52.440 line:80%
Assign him to the Armory.

00:12:53.560 --> 00:12:54.200 line:80%
Okay.

00:12:59.440 --> 00:13:00.200 line:80%
Your Lordship,

00:13:00.200 --> 00:13:03.060 line:80%
the scout in Chongzhou
sent you a challenge letter.

00:13:03.990 --> 00:13:05.180 line:80%
[To Xie, the Traitor]

00:13:19.640 --> 00:13:21.160 line:80%
Didn't I paint this?

00:13:24.600 --> 00:13:25.880 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing said

00:13:26.560 --> 00:13:28.090 line:80%
my daughter is in his hands.

00:13:29.320 --> 00:13:30.400 line:80%
Your daughter?

00:13:33.400 --> 00:13:35.060 line:80%
Fan Changning is in his hands?

00:13:54.250 --> 00:13:57.900 line:80%
[Jizhou Government Office]

00:13:58.720 --> 00:14:00.480 line:80%
Come here! Hurry!

00:14:00.680 --> 00:14:02.280 line:80%
Mother, I missed you so much.

00:14:03.680 --> 00:14:04.360 line:80%
Officer,

00:14:04.480 --> 00:14:07.200 line:80%
I heard it was the Butcher Beauty
who saved my son,

00:14:07.200 --> 00:14:08.520 line:80%
but she was put in jail.

00:14:08.880 --> 00:14:10.400 line:80%
She did nothing wrong!

00:14:10.680 --> 00:14:11.160 line:80%
Exactly!

00:14:11.160 --> 00:14:12.600 line:80%
Release our savior, the Butcher Beauty!

00:14:12.200 --> 00:14:14.540 line:80%
[Jizhou Government Office]

00:14:13.000 --> 00:14:14.600 line:80%
She did nothing wrong!

00:14:32.680 --> 00:14:33.520 line:80%
Mrs. Fan,

00:14:35.280 --> 00:14:37.140 line:80%
you don't have to force yourself.

00:14:39.440 --> 00:14:40.520 line:80%
My parents said

00:14:41.360 --> 00:14:42.400 line:80%
we must eat well

00:14:43.040 --> 00:14:44.040 line:80%
and sleep well.

00:14:45.360 --> 00:14:46.560 line:80%
Even if the sky falls,

00:14:47.120 --> 00:14:48.250 line:80%
we must keep living.

00:14:53.560 --> 00:14:54.960 line:80%
You know I can protect you

00:14:55.520 --> 00:14:57.050 line:80%
and take you away from here.

00:14:58.600 --> 00:14:59.720 line:80%
Why did you refuse?

00:15:16.320 --> 00:15:17.520 line:80%
It's been 2 months,

00:15:20.080 --> 00:15:22.140 line:80%
and I still haven't found Changning.

00:15:27.520 --> 00:15:29.880 line:80%
I don't know where else to go.

00:15:37.520 --> 00:15:39.080 line:80%
I'm so useless.

00:15:42.120 --> 00:15:45.680 line:80%
I don't even know where Changning
is suffering.

00:16:12.920 --> 00:16:15.870 line:80%
[Jizhou Government Office]

00:16:25.620 --> 00:16:28.020 line:80%
[The case is clear.]

00:16:29.840 --> 00:16:30.920 line:80%
You said

00:16:31.560 --> 00:16:33.600 line:80%
my parents were killed by bandits.

00:16:35.160 --> 00:16:36.220 line:80%
Is what you said...

00:16:37.680 --> 00:16:38.880 line:80%
true?

00:16:41.000 --> 00:16:42.120 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:16:43.480 --> 00:16:45.000 line:80%
My grandfather told me

00:16:46.680 --> 00:16:48.480 line:80%
that the day before my parents died,

00:16:48.480 --> 00:16:50.280 line:80%
they asked him to take care of us.

00:16:50.840 --> 00:16:52.280 line:80%
They knew they were going to die.

00:16:52.280 --> 00:16:53.480 line:80%
Why didn't they hide?

00:16:54.400 --> 00:16:56.600 line:80%
Why did they manage to arrange
the family assets

00:16:56.600 --> 00:16:57.720 line:80%
before dying?

00:16:59.080 --> 00:17:01.080 line:80%
Were they really killed by bandits?

00:17:01.920 --> 00:17:02.760 line:80%
Lord Li,

00:17:04.680 --> 00:17:06.139 line:80%
I want to see the case file.

00:17:07.159 --> 00:17:07.919 line:80%
It seems that these files

00:17:07.919 --> 00:17:09.520 line:80%
were indeed modified.

00:17:12.080 --> 00:17:13.159 line:80%
Grandfather sent an urgent letter

00:17:13.159 --> 00:17:13.879 line:80%
saying that this matter

00:17:13.879 --> 00:17:14.919 line:80%
is probably related to

00:17:14.919 --> 00:17:16.850 line:80%
the Jinzhou Massacre 17 years ago.

00:17:17.760 --> 00:17:19.020 line:80%
The Jinzhou Massacre?

00:17:28.119 --> 00:17:29.000 line:80%
What?

00:17:29.440 --> 00:17:31.840 line:80%
10 taels of silver isn't enough for you?

00:17:32.480 --> 00:17:33.320 line:80%
It's enough.

00:17:33.400 --> 00:17:34.120 line:80%
I mean,

00:17:34.120 --> 00:17:36.240 line:80%
if I had known she was the Butcher Beauty,

00:17:36.240 --> 00:17:38.080 line:80%
I certainly wouldn't have blamed her.

00:17:38.080 --> 00:17:38.760 line:80%
My Lord!

00:17:39.000 --> 00:17:40.760 line:80%
Please release our benefactor,
the Butcher Beauty!

00:17:40.760 --> 00:17:42.020 line:80%
She did nothing wrong!

00:17:42.200 --> 00:17:43.760 line:80%
Yes, My Lord. Please release our
benefactor, the Butcher Beauty.

00:17:43.760 --> 00:17:44.640 line:80%
Our benefactor is out!

00:17:44.640 --> 00:17:45.080 line:80%
Our benefactor is out!

00:17:45.080 --> 00:17:46.740 line:80%
Our benefactor was released!

00:17:47.840 --> 00:17:49.170 line:80%
Thank you, Benefactor!

00:17:49.200 --> 00:17:50.530 line:80%
Thank you, Benefactor!

00:17:50.760 --> 00:17:51.960 line:80%
What's wrong, Benefactor?

00:17:51.960 --> 00:17:53.280 line:80%
Why are you crying?

00:17:56.400 --> 00:17:57.480 line:80%
My younger sister

00:17:59.640 --> 00:18:00.700 line:80%
was also abducted.

00:18:01.520 --> 00:18:03.800 line:80%
And she's still nowhere to be found.

00:18:05.280 --> 00:18:07.810 line:80%
Well, everyone has moments
of carelessness.

00:18:08.000 --> 00:18:09.760 line:80%
I was also careless,

00:18:09.840 --> 00:18:11.800 line:80%
which is how I lost my girl.

00:18:12.000 --> 00:18:13.460 line:80%
Everyone makes mistakes.

00:18:13.680 --> 00:18:14.640 line:80%
Your sister

00:18:14.640 --> 00:18:16.120 line:80%
will definitely be found.

00:18:16.200 --> 00:18:18.130 line:80%
Good things happen to good people.

00:18:19.000 --> 00:18:20.480 line:80%
A mistake is a mistake.

00:18:22.200 --> 00:18:24.860 line:80%
If you lose a child
due to your own carelessness,

00:18:25.080 --> 00:18:27.140 line:80%
how can you easily forgive yourself?

00:18:28.520 --> 00:18:30.320 line:80%
If you don't remember this time,

00:18:30.600 --> 00:18:32.400 line:80%
you'll lose her again next time!

00:18:41.800 --> 00:18:43.660 line:80%
I should learn a lesson from this.

00:18:52.240 --> 00:18:52.770 line:80%
Mrs. Fan.

00:18:54.440 --> 00:18:57.370 line:80%
Didn't you want to see
the file on your parents' case?

00:18:58.000 --> 00:18:58.800 line:80%
I found them.

00:19:01.450 --> 00:19:04.140 line:80%
[Government Office]

00:19:11.400 --> 00:19:12.160 line:80%
Mrs. Fan,

00:19:12.560 --> 00:19:15.090 line:80%
this is the file
on your family's murder case.

00:19:17.640 --> 00:19:18.560 line:80%
Will it cause trouble for you

00:19:18.560 --> 00:19:20.760 line:80%
now that I'm looking into this, My Lord?

00:19:30.800 --> 00:19:32.930 line:80%
I don't know some of these characters.

00:19:35.040 --> 00:19:36.160 line:80%
Which ones?

00:19:38.040 --> 00:19:38.800 line:80%
This one.

00:19:38.550 --> 00:19:39.080 line:80%
[In October of the 16th year of Yongping,]

00:19:39.100 --> 00:19:40.150 line:80%
[Fan Erniu of Lin'an Town and his wife
were traveling together]

00:19:40.000 --> 00:19:41.040 line:80%
This. And this.

00:19:40.180 --> 00:19:40.920 line:80%
[when they were killed on the road.]

00:19:41.600 --> 00:19:42.360 line:80%
I know this one,

00:19:42.360 --> 00:19:43.620 line:80%
but none of the others.

00:19:46.600 --> 00:19:47.800 line:80%
Let me read it for you.

00:19:47.880 --> 00:19:48.560 line:80%
Thank you.

00:19:52.800 --> 00:19:55.000 line:80%
In October of the 16th year of Yongping,

00:19:56.240 --> 00:19:59.640 line:80%
Fan Erniu of Lin'an Town and his wife
were traveling together

00:20:00.760 --> 00:20:02.760 line:80%
when they were killed on the road.

00:20:03.400 --> 00:20:05.600 line:80%
Fan Erniu, male, 45 years old,

00:20:06.240 --> 00:20:07.770 line:80%
wearing a gray short shirt.

00:20:08.560 --> 00:20:11.760 line:80%
There were multiple stab wounds
to his chest and abdomen.

00:20:12.400 --> 00:20:14.000 line:80%
The evidence is conclusive.

00:20:14.840 --> 00:20:17.100 line:80%
Men have been sent to arrest the culprit.

00:20:21.600 --> 00:20:22.560 line:80%
I thought

00:20:23.400 --> 00:20:25.240 line:80%
I could find clues in the file.

00:20:26.120 --> 00:20:27.380 line:80%
It turns out my parents

00:20:27.440 --> 00:20:29.170 line:80%
were really killed by bandits.

00:20:31.400 --> 00:20:33.600 line:80%
Even if it wasn't the Qingfeng Stronghold,

00:20:33.600 --> 00:20:35.400 line:80%
it must have been other bandits.

00:20:36.600 --> 00:20:37.440 line:80%
Mrs. Fan.

00:20:38.440 --> 00:20:39.970 line:80%
The past cannot be changed,

00:20:40.240 --> 00:20:41.770 line:80%
but the future still can be.

00:20:45.200 --> 00:20:46.160 line:80%
Mrs. Fan.

00:20:47.080 --> 00:20:47.880 line:80%
Here is your bundle.

00:20:47.880 --> 00:20:49.540 line:80%
Check if anything is missing.

00:20:53.660 --> 00:20:57.480 line:80%
[Divorce Agreement]

00:21:03.120 --> 00:21:05.580 line:80%
What are your plans for the future,
Mrs. Fan?

00:21:06.120 --> 00:21:08.120 line:80%
I want to find Changning
as soon as possible.

00:21:08.120 --> 00:21:09.280 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao is still in Lin'an,

00:21:09.280 --> 00:21:11.080 line:80%
waiting for me to bring her back.

00:21:14.080 --> 00:21:15.080 line:80%
And Yan Zheng.

00:21:16.400 --> 00:21:17.930 line:80%
Whether he's dead or alive,

00:21:18.600 --> 00:21:19.680 line:80%
I will find him.

00:21:22.320 --> 00:21:23.320 line:80%
Why don't you...

00:21:24.160 --> 00:21:25.520 line:80%
stay here

00:21:25.880 --> 00:21:27.810 line:80%
and let me help you find Changning?

00:21:28.880 --> 00:21:29.920 line:80%
The war is coming.

00:21:30.560 --> 00:21:32.120 line:80%
You must be very busy, My Lord.

00:21:32.120 --> 00:21:33.160 line:80%
This is my family matter,

00:21:33.160 --> 00:21:34.420 line:80%
so I won't trouble you.

00:21:37.320 --> 00:21:38.040 line:80%
Well then,

00:21:38.720 --> 00:21:40.520 line:80%
if you need my help in the future,

00:21:40.520 --> 00:21:41.320 line:80%
just ask.

00:21:41.320 --> 00:21:42.250 line:80%
Don't hold back.

00:21:43.440 --> 00:21:45.400 line:80%
Thank you for your sincere help, My Lord.

00:21:45.400 --> 00:21:46.600 line:80%
You previously

00:21:47.120 --> 00:21:48.720 line:80%
paid 10 taels of silver for me.

00:21:48.720 --> 00:21:50.180 line:80%
I have prepared the money.

00:21:50.840 --> 00:21:52.120 line:80%
Some time ago,

00:21:52.560 --> 00:21:53.840 line:80%
I helped the Lin'an Government Office

00:21:53.840 --> 00:21:55.840 line:80%
destroy several trafficking dens.

00:21:56.120 --> 00:21:57.600 line:80%
Although it wasn't a great achievement,

00:21:57.600 --> 00:21:59.800 line:80%
the office gave me a reward.

00:22:00.760 --> 00:22:01.880 line:80%
It's at the posthouse.

00:22:01.880 --> 00:22:03.740 line:80%
I'll bring it to you when I go back.

00:22:05.440 --> 00:22:06.120 line:80%
Alright.

00:22:07.120 --> 00:22:07.800 line:80%
Servants.

00:22:08.480 --> 00:22:10.480 line:80%
Send Mrs. Fan back to the posthouse.

00:22:10.480 --> 00:22:11.120 line:80%
Please.

00:22:18.600 --> 00:22:20.240 line:80%
Should we report Mrs. Fan's matter

00:22:20.240 --> 00:22:21.280 line:80%
to Lord He?

00:22:21.320 --> 00:22:22.840 line:80%
Even Mrs. Fan knows war is imminent

00:22:22.840 --> 00:22:25.000 line:80%
and we shouldn't disturb
the army's morale.

00:22:25.000 --> 00:22:26.840 line:80%
Master is the commander-in-chief,
after all.

00:22:26.840 --> 00:22:28.440 line:80%
Let's not bother him.

00:22:32.720 --> 00:22:33.320 line:80%
My Lord,

00:22:33.640 --> 00:22:36.240 line:80%
there's an urgent letter
from the Grand Tutor.

00:22:44.520 --> 00:22:45.840 line:80%
After the grain route was destroyed,

00:22:45.840 --> 00:22:48.040 line:80%
Lord Changxin indeed couldn't hold out

00:22:48.120 --> 00:22:49.780 line:80%
and retreated to Hongdaokou.

00:22:50.920 --> 00:22:51.680 line:80%
Next,

00:22:51.880 --> 00:22:53.000 line:80%
the rainy season is coming.

00:22:53.000 --> 00:22:54.280 line:80%
The streams will change course,

00:22:54.280 --> 00:22:56.120 line:80%
and the mountain roads
will be hard to travel.

00:22:56.120 --> 00:22:58.400 line:80%
If Lord Changxin sends troops south,

00:22:59.000 --> 00:23:01.330 line:80%
they will inevitably pass through Baxia.

00:23:04.520 --> 00:23:06.600 line:80%
It's time to meet He Jingyuan.

00:23:07.120 --> 00:23:09.120 line:80%
Downstream of the Wu River is Baxia.

00:23:09.440 --> 00:23:11.480 line:80%
The rainy season is approaching.

00:23:12.080 --> 00:23:14.320 line:80%
General He, you can lead men upstream

00:23:13.660 --> 00:23:18.620 line:80%
[Break the Enemy's Stronghold]

00:23:14.320 --> 00:23:16.250 line:80%
to build a dam at a hidden location.

00:23:16.480 --> 00:23:18.810 line:80%
His Lordship will act as bait downstream.

00:23:19.120 --> 00:23:20.840 line:80%
If the rebel army falls for the trap,

00:23:20.840 --> 00:23:22.480 line:80%
they will surely suffer heavy losses.

00:23:22.480 --> 00:23:24.880 line:80%
This plan
can relieve the siege of Lucheng.

00:23:27.000 --> 00:23:28.680 line:80%
A flood attack?

00:23:29.000 --> 00:23:30.600 line:80%
It is a brilliant plan,

00:23:31.600 --> 00:23:34.920 line:80%
but having His Lordship
risk his life as bait...

00:23:35.080 --> 00:23:37.160 line:80%
What if something goes wrong?

00:23:38.520 --> 00:23:39.850 line:80%
If the bait is too small,

00:23:40.400 --> 00:23:43.200 line:80%
I fear a crafty man like Sui Yuanqing
won't take it.

00:23:45.640 --> 00:23:46.880 line:80%
If you trust me,

00:23:47.800 --> 00:23:49.800 line:80%
lend me 1000 troops

00:23:50.440 --> 00:23:52.570 line:80%
before the main Yanzhou army arrives.

00:23:53.040 --> 00:23:54.680 line:80%
1000 troops?

00:23:55.000 --> 00:23:56.000 line:80%
Do you know

00:23:56.320 --> 00:23:58.040 line:80%
that Sui Yuanqing has 20,000 troops

00:23:58.040 --> 00:23:59.880 line:80%
stationed in Baxia?

00:24:00.400 --> 00:24:01.440 line:80%
With too many troops,

00:24:01.440 --> 00:24:03.300 line:80%
it might be inconvenient to flee.

00:24:10.680 --> 00:24:12.140 line:80%
A tactic to lure the enemy?

00:24:12.880 --> 00:24:16.440 line:80%
Your Lordship, you're unparalleled
in wisdom and bravery.

00:24:16.960 --> 00:24:18.560 line:80%
Okay. I agree.

00:24:20.120 --> 00:24:22.120 line:80%
Thank you, General He.

00:24:22.520 --> 00:24:25.040 line:80%
If we can relieve the siege of Lucheng

00:24:25.360 --> 00:24:26.720 line:80%
and save Jizhou,

00:24:26.960 --> 00:24:29.560 line:80%
I should be the one thanking you two.

00:24:32.960 --> 00:24:34.240 line:80%
Thank you, General.

00:24:37.280 --> 00:24:38.080 line:80%
General,

00:24:39.120 --> 00:24:40.960 line:80%
I have one more request

00:24:41.080 --> 00:24:42.240 line:80%
on this visit.

00:24:42.240 --> 00:24:43.000 line:80%
Speak.

00:24:45.600 --> 00:24:47.200 line:80%
I'd like to speak in private.

00:24:48.080 --> 00:24:49.400 line:80%
You may leave.

00:24:49.520 --> 00:24:50.240 line:80%
Yes!

00:24:53.560 --> 00:24:54.920 line:80%
Here. Please.

00:25:01.400 --> 00:25:02.280 line:80%
General He,

00:25:03.000 --> 00:25:05.480 line:80%
my direct attack on Baxia

00:25:06.200 --> 00:25:07.530 line:80%
is also to save someone.

00:25:08.160 --> 00:25:11.400 line:80%
The heir apparent of Lord Changxin
kidnapped my wife's sister.

00:25:11.400 --> 00:25:12.800 line:80%
I must save her.

00:25:13.000 --> 00:25:14.130 line:80%
Your wife's sister?

00:25:15.280 --> 00:25:16.960 line:80%
Changning was kidnapped?

00:25:22.760 --> 00:25:24.120 line:80%
It seems you already know

00:25:24.120 --> 00:25:26.520 line:80%
about my relationship with the Fan family.

00:25:27.840 --> 00:25:29.560 line:80%
May I ask—

00:25:29.840 --> 00:25:32.040 line:80%
do you know the details

00:25:32.600 --> 00:25:34.240 line:80%
of the Fans' murder case?

00:25:36.760 --> 00:25:38.400 line:80%
You're too direct.

00:25:46.400 --> 00:25:47.280 line:80%
General He?

00:25:52.760 --> 00:25:54.080 line:80%
Actually,

00:25:54.360 --> 00:25:58.840 line:80%
Fan Erniu and I were friends
in the same camp.

00:26:00.800 --> 00:26:03.560 line:80%
Before he died, he gave me a letter,

00:26:04.000 --> 00:26:06.000 line:80%
asking me to deliver it
to Prime Minister Wei

00:26:06.000 --> 00:26:09.800 line:80%
and warning me never to open it.

00:26:10.840 --> 00:26:12.000 line:80%
So,

00:26:12.160 --> 00:26:13.960 line:80%
did you kill your old friend

00:26:13.960 --> 00:26:15.890 line:80%
to make Prime Minister Wei believe

00:26:16.560 --> 00:26:18.400 line:80%
that you were still loyal to him?

00:26:24.640 --> 00:26:25.280 line:80%
No.

00:26:25.760 --> 00:26:27.600 line:80%
Fan committed suicide.

00:26:28.720 --> 00:26:31.240 line:80%
But it was after I arrived.

00:26:31.240 --> 00:26:34.560 line:80%
You could say I forced him to do it.

00:26:37.400 --> 00:26:38.800 line:80%
If I hadn't gone,

00:26:39.600 --> 00:26:42.320 line:80%
Prime Minister Wei
would have sent someone else.

00:26:42.320 --> 00:26:43.960 line:80%
By then,

00:26:44.160 --> 00:26:46.720 line:80%
they would have wiped out
the entire family.

00:26:51.800 --> 00:26:55.200 line:80%
Since ancient times, loyalty and
righteousness have been hard to reconcile.

00:26:55.200 --> 00:26:57.330 line:80%
It's not entirely your fault, Lord He.

00:26:57.360 --> 00:26:59.200 line:80%
But they have already gone.

00:26:59.960 --> 00:27:03.840 line:80%
I feel guilty.

00:27:05.920 --> 00:27:07.480 line:80%
The father of the Fan girls

00:27:07.920 --> 00:27:09.650 line:80%
wasn't named Fan Erniu, was he?

00:27:10.000 --> 00:27:11.260 line:80%
What was his real name?

00:27:12.080 --> 00:27:15.140 line:80%
And what position did he hold
under the Prime Minister?

00:27:15.560 --> 00:27:16.680 line:80%
Your Lordship,

00:27:17.040 --> 00:27:18.040 line:80%
I absolutely

00:27:18.800 --> 00:27:20.720 line:80%
cannot tell you about this,

00:27:21.600 --> 00:27:26.320 line:80%
at least not until
the Fan sisters are safe.

00:27:26.320 --> 00:27:30.360 line:80%
And I will tell Mrs. Fan myself.

00:27:36.440 --> 00:27:39.360 line:80%
Please spread the word for me.

00:27:39.520 --> 00:27:40.600 line:80%
Just say

00:27:41.000 --> 00:27:42.960 line:80%
that the girl captured
by Lord Changxin's heir apparent

00:27:42.960 --> 00:27:44.360 line:80%
is my daughter.

00:27:45.000 --> 00:27:46.860 line:80%
And I will definitely rescue her.

00:27:47.160 --> 00:27:48.120 line:80%
Your Lordship,

00:27:49.280 --> 00:27:51.400 line:80%
what's the meaning of this?

00:27:51.480 --> 00:27:53.480 line:80%
It's called beating them
at their own game.

00:27:53.480 --> 00:27:54.320 line:80%
First,

00:27:54.600 --> 00:27:55.840 line:80%
Lord Changxin's heir apparent

00:27:55.840 --> 00:27:57.560 line:80%
will believe that His Lordship
is desperate to save his daughter,

00:27:57.560 --> 00:27:58.600 line:80%
venturing into danger alone,

00:27:58.600 --> 00:28:00.060 line:80%
so he will lower his guard.

00:28:00.160 --> 00:28:01.040 line:80%
Second,

00:28:01.680 --> 00:28:02.920 line:80%
Lord Changxin's heir apparent

00:28:02.920 --> 00:28:04.640 line:80%
knows his hostage is valuable.

00:28:04.640 --> 00:28:07.320 line:80%
Changning won't be in danger of dying.

00:28:09.880 --> 00:28:12.540 line:80%
You have thought of everything,
Your Lordship.

00:28:12.960 --> 00:28:16.080 line:80%
I leave Changning in your hands.

00:28:16.080 --> 00:28:19.360 line:80%
Otherwise, I cannot face my old friend.

00:28:21.120 --> 00:28:22.450 line:80%
Rest assured, General.

00:28:23.160 --> 00:28:25.000 line:80%
I will bring her back safely.

00:28:30.880 --> 00:28:33.480 line:80%
Fate really plays tricks on us.

00:28:36.560 --> 00:28:37.280 line:80%
General.

00:28:38.400 --> 00:28:39.960 line:80%
Pei Yi, come here.

00:28:44.040 --> 00:28:46.400 line:80%
There is a heinous task

00:28:46.600 --> 00:28:49.530 line:80%
that might bring condemnation
from the whole world.

00:28:49.800 --> 00:28:52.360 line:80%
Will you do it or not?

00:28:53.520 --> 00:28:55.800 line:80%
You saved my life, General.

00:28:56.320 --> 00:28:58.400 line:80%
Every day I live is a bonus.

00:28:58.800 --> 00:29:00.360 line:80%
Reputation is nothing to me.

00:29:00.360 --> 00:29:01.690 line:80%
Please speak, General.

00:29:04.240 --> 00:29:04.840 line:80%
Come.

00:29:09.040 --> 00:29:12.500 line:80%
Lord Changxin's army
wants to attack during the rainy season,

00:29:12.680 --> 00:29:14.680 line:80%
so they must pass through Baxia.

00:29:19.620 --> 00:29:23.170 line:80%
[Northwest Inn]

00:29:22.240 --> 00:29:23.320 line:80%
Butcher Beauty.

00:29:23.400 --> 00:29:24.930 line:80%
Butcher Beauty, slow down!

00:29:25.120 --> 00:29:26.480 line:80%
It's over in Chongzhou, right?

00:29:26.480 --> 00:29:27.160 line:80%
Yes.

00:29:27.360 --> 00:29:29.760 line:80%
I heard it
when I was looking for my child.

00:29:29.800 --> 00:29:31.160 line:80%
There is a refugee camp in Baxia.

00:29:31.160 --> 00:29:32.520 line:80%
They took in many children.

00:29:32.520 --> 00:29:33.840 line:80%
You should go there and look for her.

00:29:33.840 --> 00:29:35.370 line:80%
See if your sister is there.

00:29:36.760 --> 00:29:37.840 line:80%
Go west, right?

00:29:38.000 --> 00:29:40.530 line:80%
Yes. Pass through Baxia,
and you'll be there.

00:29:40.710 --> 00:29:43.090 line:80%
[Jizhou Government Office]

00:29:43.200 --> 00:29:44.760 line:80%
What happened to Wei Qilin

00:29:44.760 --> 00:29:47.400 line:80%
was likely a setup by Wei Yan

00:29:45.800 --> 00:29:53.090 line:80%
[Peace at the border]

00:29:47.640 --> 00:29:49.640 line:80%
to cover up scandals from back then.

00:29:50.200 --> 00:29:52.760 line:80%
Wei Yan not only abuses power,

00:29:53.080 --> 00:29:55.600 line:80%
but also forces loyal generals
to their deaths

00:29:55.600 --> 00:29:57.440 line:80%
for his own selfish interests.

00:29:57.960 --> 00:30:00.420 line:80%
It shows just how cunning and ruthless
he is.

00:30:01.280 --> 00:30:03.560 line:80%
Now the war is imminent,

00:30:03.880 --> 00:30:07.600 line:80%
and the position of Discipline Inspector
in the Jizhou Army is still vacant.

00:30:07.600 --> 00:30:09.120 line:80%
You could join the army

00:30:09.120 --> 00:30:10.680 line:80%
and work to dismantle the Wei faction.

00:30:10.680 --> 00:30:13.080 line:80%
Do not delay upon seeing this letter.

00:30:13.240 --> 00:30:15.440 line:80%
Go immediately to the front
to deliver supplies,

00:30:15.440 --> 00:30:16.800 line:80%
stabilize the troops,

00:30:16.920 --> 00:30:18.920 line:80%
and seek your post.

00:30:21.480 --> 00:30:22.120 line:80%
My Lord.

00:30:22.720 --> 00:30:24.520 line:80%
Mrs. Fan has left the posthouse.

00:30:24.640 --> 00:30:25.960 line:80%
She asked someone
to leave 10 taels of silver,

00:30:25.960 --> 00:30:27.080 line:80%
saying she wanted to pay you back.

00:30:27.080 --> 00:30:28.280 line:80%
I looked everywhere,

00:30:28.560 --> 00:30:29.890 line:80%
but I couldn't find her.

00:30:36.600 --> 00:30:38.480 line:80%
Although you want to help Mrs. Fan,

00:30:38.480 --> 00:30:40.000 line:80%
the war cannot be delayed.

00:30:43.760 --> 00:30:46.600 line:80%
[Peace at the border]

00:30:52.540 --> 00:30:55.310 line:80%
[Government Office]

00:30:52.960 --> 00:30:53.600 line:80%
My Lord!

00:31:00.680 --> 00:31:01.240 line:80%
Changyu!

00:31:09.120 --> 00:31:10.200 line:80%
Please forgive my rudeness, miss.

00:31:10.200 --> 00:31:11.930 line:80%
I mistook you for someone else.

00:31:17.600 --> 00:31:18.920 line:80%
Leave two men here.

00:31:19.200 --> 00:31:20.600 line:80%
If she comes back looking for her sister,

00:31:20.600 --> 00:31:22.000 line:80%
tell her which way I went.

00:31:22.360 --> 00:31:23.040 line:80%
Yes.

00:31:31.480 --> 00:31:32.160 line:80%
Let's go!

00:31:35.340 --> 00:31:38.020 line:80%
[Jizhou Government Office]

00:31:44.640 --> 00:31:45.720 line:80%
Eldest Young Master,

00:31:45.720 --> 00:31:48.850 line:80%
the Little Young Master
wants you to check his homework.

00:31:51.880 --> 00:31:52.800 line:80%
Bring him in.

00:31:56.200 --> 00:31:57.730 line:80%
Little Young Master, come.

00:32:36.160 --> 00:32:38.120 line:80%
What kind of crap is this?

00:32:38.160 --> 00:32:40.290 line:80%
The handwriting is weak and boneless.

00:32:41.240 --> 00:32:42.120 line:80%
Rewrite it.

00:32:42.800 --> 00:32:43.480 line:80%
Dad...

00:32:44.520 --> 00:32:46.480 line:80%
Fa-Father.

00:32:48.160 --> 00:32:49.640 line:80%
After I finish writing,

00:32:50.680 --> 00:32:52.600 line:80%
can I go see my mother?

00:32:54.160 --> 00:32:55.240 line:80%
What did you say?

00:32:56.920 --> 00:32:58.250 line:80%
After I finish writing,

00:32:59.560 --> 00:33:01.640 line:80%
can I go see my mother?

00:33:06.560 --> 00:33:08.000 line:80%
Who allowed you

00:33:09.160 --> 00:33:10.600 line:80%
to call me Father?

00:33:15.960 --> 00:33:17.620 line:80%
What does your mother usually

00:33:18.440 --> 00:33:19.960 line:80%
say about your father?

00:33:21.640 --> 00:33:22.640 line:80%
My mother says

00:33:23.960 --> 00:33:25.480 line:80%
Father is a great hero.

00:33:26.840 --> 00:33:29.520 line:80%
If one day you're caught by bad guys,

00:33:30.160 --> 00:33:32.600 line:80%
there will surely be someone asking
who your daddy is.

00:33:32.600 --> 00:33:33.960 line:80%
Just tell them

00:33:33.960 --> 00:33:35.800 line:80%
your daddy is a great hero.

00:33:35.960 --> 00:33:38.320 line:80%
My dad really is a great hero?

00:33:38.320 --> 00:33:39.440 line:80%
He's nothing.

00:33:41.360 --> 00:33:43.840 line:80%
But saying this can save your life.

00:33:44.640 --> 00:33:46.360 line:80%
You must be absolutely sincere

00:33:46.360 --> 00:33:48.520 line:80%
when you say your daddy is a great hero.

00:33:48.960 --> 00:33:49.760 line:80%
Got it?

00:33:52.800 --> 00:33:55.400 line:80%
Your mother taught you to say this,
didn't she?

00:33:57.440 --> 00:33:59.560 line:80%
My mother always tells me this.

00:34:00.400 --> 00:34:01.840 line:80%
What else did she say?

00:34:03.920 --> 00:34:07.400 line:80%
Daddy is a great hero
who does great things.

00:34:07.520 --> 00:34:09.519 line:80%
He... he loves us very much.

00:34:11.240 --> 00:34:14.400 line:80%
But Daddy has to look after the country,

00:34:14.479 --> 00:34:17.120 line:80%
so he can't come to see us often.

00:34:24.640 --> 00:34:25.800 line:80%
Little brat.

00:34:26.519 --> 00:34:28.850 line:80%
Not a word of truth
comes out of your mouth.

00:34:29.479 --> 00:34:31.519 line:80%
Your mother is a big liar,

00:34:31.840 --> 00:34:33.920 line:80%
and you are a little liar.

00:34:39.600 --> 00:34:40.800 line:80%
But I like hearing it.

00:34:42.640 --> 00:34:44.240 line:80%
Practice your handwriting.

00:35:21.200 --> 00:35:22.930 line:80%
Spare me, Eldest Young Master!

00:35:23.320 --> 00:35:25.180 line:80%
Drag her out and beat her to death.

00:35:25.320 --> 00:35:26.760 line:80%
-Yes.
-Spare me, Eldest Young Master!

00:35:26.760 --> 00:35:28.240 line:80%
Spare me, Eldest Young Master!

00:35:28.240 --> 00:35:29.970 line:80%
Spare me, Eldest Young Master!

00:35:31.640 --> 00:35:33.320 line:80%
Spare me, Eldest Young Master!

00:35:33.320 --> 00:35:35.920 line:80%
Eldest Young Master, I was wrong!

00:35:37.000 --> 00:35:38.400 line:80%
I know I was wrong!

00:35:39.560 --> 00:35:41.400 line:80%
Spare me, Eldest Young Master!

00:35:41.880 --> 00:35:44.000 line:80%
Spare me, Eldest Young Master!

00:35:47.880 --> 00:35:50.320 line:80%
Spare me, Eldest Young Master!

00:35:50.320 --> 00:35:52.760 line:80%
Spare me, Eldest Young Master!

00:35:54.720 --> 00:35:56.450 line:80%
Spare me, Eldest Young Master!

00:36:00.000 --> 00:36:01.880 line:80%
I won't dare do it again!

00:36:05.760 --> 00:36:07.640 line:80%
Bao'er!

00:36:10.480 --> 00:36:12.360 line:80%
Spare me, Eldest Young Master!

00:36:17.560 --> 00:36:19.320 line:80%
Spare me, Eldest Young Master!

00:36:24.400 --> 00:36:25.600 line:80%
Eldest Young Master!

00:36:52.880 --> 00:36:53.960 line:80%
Is your daddy

00:36:54.920 --> 00:36:56.560 line:80%
still a great hero?

00:36:59.360 --> 00:37:01.160 line:80%
Daddy is a great hero...

00:37:01.560 --> 00:37:03.560 line:80%
Daddy is a great hero...

00:37:04.240 --> 00:37:06.440 line:80%
Daddy is a great hero...

00:37:09.120 --> 00:37:10.880 line:80%
Daddy is a great hero...

00:37:13.800 --> 00:37:14.920 line:80%
Keep practicing.

00:37:38.800 --> 00:37:40.000 line:80%
It's already spring.

00:37:40.520 --> 00:37:42.450 line:80%
Why is the stream still so shallow?

00:37:46.800 --> 00:37:47.840 line:80%
Help, miss!

00:37:48.200 --> 00:37:49.200 line:80%
Help, miss!

00:37:50.960 --> 00:37:51.480 line:80%
Miss!

00:37:56.280 --> 00:37:57.480 line:80%
You ran into bandits?

00:38:00.200 --> 00:38:00.880 line:80%
Miss,

00:38:00.960 --> 00:38:02.120 line:80%
I'm not a bad person.

00:38:02.640 --> 00:38:04.640 line:80%
The officials are heartless.

00:38:04.680 --> 00:38:07.410 line:80%
They're forcing us good people
to quarry stones.

00:38:11.400 --> 00:38:12.720 line:80%
I need to hide in the woods.

00:38:12.720 --> 00:38:13.920 line:80%
Don't tell them where I went.

00:38:13.920 --> 00:38:15.380 line:80%
I have a family to support.

00:38:15.400 --> 00:38:16.400 line:80%
If they catch me,

00:38:16.480 --> 00:38:18.520 line:80%
I probably won't survive!

00:38:24.040 --> 00:38:24.400 line:80%
Hyah!

00:38:24.760 --> 00:38:25.120 line:80%
Hyah!

00:38:25.120 --> 00:38:25.760 line:80%
Hyah!

00:38:27.960 --> 00:38:28.680 line:80%
Whoa!

00:38:29.240 --> 00:38:29.880 line:80%
Miss,

00:38:30.160 --> 00:38:31.490 line:80%
did you see a man pass by?

00:38:32.320 --> 00:38:32.920 line:80%
I did.

00:38:32.920 --> 00:38:34.120 line:80%
Which way did he go?

00:38:34.760 --> 00:38:35.560 line:80%
That way.

00:38:39.720 --> 00:38:40.600 line:80%
You two,

00:38:40.720 --> 00:38:41.960 line:80%
keep chasing down that road.

00:38:41.960 --> 00:38:43.400 line:80%
The rest of you, follow me!

00:38:43.400 --> 00:38:43.920 line:80%
Yes!

00:38:44.440 --> 00:38:45.120 line:80%
Hyah!

00:38:46.040 --> 00:38:46.560 line:80%
Hyah!

00:38:56.240 --> 00:38:58.480 line:80%
I thank you
on behalf of my whole family, miss.

00:38:58.480 --> 00:38:59.480 line:80%
Thank you, miss.

00:38:59.600 --> 00:39:00.600 line:80%
Thank you, miss.

00:39:05.080 --> 00:39:06.080 line:80%
It was nothing.

00:39:06.760 --> 00:39:07.820 line:80%
No need to thank me.

00:39:08.360 --> 00:39:09.080 line:80%
Miss,

00:39:09.600 --> 00:39:10.730 line:80%
do you have any food?

00:39:10.960 --> 00:39:13.080 line:80%
I haven't eaten in days.

00:39:14.400 --> 00:39:15.400 line:80%
I'll get you some.

00:39:38.960 --> 00:39:40.080 line:80%
Trying to ambush me?

00:39:40.080 --> 00:39:41.480 line:80%
Do you think I'm a pushover?

00:39:41.480 --> 00:39:42.040 line:80%
When...

00:39:42.440 --> 00:39:44.160 line:80%
When did you find out?

00:39:44.320 --> 00:39:46.320 line:80%
I heard iron clash in your sleeve.

00:39:46.480 --> 00:39:47.810 line:80%
It was clearly a dagger.

00:39:47.840 --> 00:39:49.360 line:80%
You must have wanted to steal my horse

00:39:49.360 --> 00:39:50.160 line:80%
to escape.

00:39:51.560 --> 00:39:52.240 line:80%
Hyah!

00:39:52.680 --> 00:39:53.320 line:80%
Hyah!

00:39:56.040 --> 00:39:56.720 line:80%
Hyah!

00:40:01.040 --> 00:40:02.280 line:80%
Why did you lie to me?

00:40:02.560 --> 00:40:03.080 line:80%
Sir,

00:40:03.280 --> 00:40:05.040 line:80%
I was deceived by this man just now.

00:40:05.040 --> 00:40:06.840 line:80%
He said he had a family to support

00:40:06.920 --> 00:40:08.440 line:80%
and asked me
not to reveal his whereabouts.

00:40:08.440 --> 00:40:10.560 line:80%
He even tried to attack me just now,

00:40:10.560 --> 00:40:11.560 line:80%
but I subdued him.

00:40:12.440 --> 00:40:13.100 line:80%
Tie them up.

00:40:13.440 --> 00:40:14.360 line:80%
Take them both.

00:40:15.480 --> 00:40:16.120 line:80%
Sir,

00:40:16.360 --> 00:40:17.440 line:80%
I'm innocent.

00:40:17.480 --> 00:40:19.280 line:80%
I didn't know the truth earlier.

00:40:19.320 --> 00:40:21.280 line:80%
But I subdued him.

00:40:21.280 --> 00:40:22.280 line:80%
Consider it an act of atonement

00:40:22.280 --> 00:40:23.560 line:80%
and spare me.

00:40:23.720 --> 00:40:25.560 line:80%
He's a scout from Chongzhou.

00:40:25.960 --> 00:40:28.400 line:80%
Maybe you're a rebel from Chongzhou too,

00:40:28.760 --> 00:40:31.040 line:80%
seeing that
you couldn't take this scout away

00:40:31.040 --> 00:40:33.300 line:80%
and conspired to stage this whole thing.

00:40:34.480 --> 00:40:36.810 line:80%
I have my household registration papers.

00:40:37.000 --> 00:40:38.920 line:80%
Sir, I'm from Jizhou.

00:40:43.720 --> 00:40:45.080 line:80%
If you're from Jizhou,

00:40:45.720 --> 00:40:47.320 line:80%
and it's currently wartime,

00:40:47.800 --> 00:40:50.240 line:80%
why are you running towards Chongzhou?

00:40:53.840 --> 00:40:55.400 line:80%
We'll verify your identity

00:40:55.640 --> 00:40:57.280 line:80%
after we get back.

00:40:58.240 --> 00:40:59.100 line:80%
Take them away!

00:41:00.080 --> 00:41:00.640 line:80%
Move!